      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "ta: Rangi/ Es atinettifchnu tewi\nno tahs Semmes Wirfus/ tchin-\nni Gaddâ tu nomirft/ jo tu effi\nweenu Atkahpschanu runnajs\nprett to KUNGU."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta nomirre tas Pra-\nweets Kananijus tanni Gaddâ\nfeptitâ Mehnefi."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXIX. Nodalla.\nJeremijus mahza tohs Zeetumneekus eekſch\nBabeles zaur weenu Grahmatu: i. Ra\nteem zaur jawu Apzeetinaschanas kaiku buhs\nturretees: 5. Un fa tam kaikam pahri ne\nbuhs buht pahr jeptindejmits Gaddeem: 10.\nPapreekschfluddinaschana no to Atlifkofchu\nNelaimibas: 16. Un no tahs Bohjâ.Ee,\nschanas daschu wiltigu Praweeschu: 21) 31.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "IN fchee irr tee Wahrdi\ntahs Grahmatas/ ko tas\nPraweets Jeremijus\nfuhtiia no Jerusalemes uhs teem\natlikkuscheem Wezzajeem / kas\naiswesti bija/ un us teem Pree-\nstereem / un us teem Prawee-\nscheem/ un us wiſſeem Laudun/\nto Nebukadnezars bij no Jeru-\nsalemes uhs Babeli weddis."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz fa Jekantjustas Keh-\nninsch/ un ta Kehnininne/un tee\nKanbar-Junkuri / un tee Feel-\nkungi no Juha un Jerusale-\nmes/ lihds ar teem Remmescheem\nun Kallejeem no Jerusalemes\nnobst bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zaur to Robku Eleasa Sa-\nwana Dehla/ un Geimartjus Il-\nkjus Dehla / ko Zedekijus tas\nKehninsch no Juha us Babeli\nfuhtiia pee Nebukadnezara ta\nhnina no Babeles/ un fazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zebaot/ tas Israëta Deews /\nwiffeem Aiswesteem/ kas no\nrusalemes irr uhs Babeli ai\nwesti:"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ustaisajt Nammus/\ndshwojeet(eeksch teem/)un de\nstait-Dahrsus / un ehdeet\nwinnu Augkeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nemmeet Seewas /\ndseundinajeet Dehlus un Meita\nun nemmeet juhſeem Dehlee\nSeewas/ un dohdeet juhf\nMeitas Wihreem/ ka tee De\nlus un Meitas dseundina /\nwairojtees tur/ un ne tohpe\nmasaki."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un meklejeet ta Pilsfah\nLabklahschann/ korp es juhs e\nmu lizzis aiswest/ un peeluhdse\nto KUNG U winna deht/\neekſch winna Meeru stahw\njuhsu Labklahschana."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta takka tas KUNG\nZebaot/ tas Israëta Deewe\nLaid juhsu Praweeschi/ un juh\nSthineeki/ tas juhsu Widdii\njuhs ne peeivilt/ un ne klauja\njuhſeem Sapnotajeem/ fo ju\nleekat Sapnoht."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee fluddina jums Ma\ntus eekſch manna Wahrdai /\ntohs ne etmu fuhtijs / takka ta\nKUNG:"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta takka tas KUNG\nTeefcham / kad feptindeſmi\nGaddi Babelê buhs pa Gallan\ntad peemeklefchu es juhs/ un fi\nchu jums notieft pehz mani\nschehliga Wahrdai / un atweo"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
